<paragraph id="829A4434AC961CE47EE1556CFEEC5702" pageId="2" pageNumber="69">Type specimens.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CE21BDF8CF5CD3B6CF8C74F7F74FED30" pageId="2" pageNumber="69">
Holotype. Kunming Natural History Museum of Zoology, Kunming Institute of Zoology, Chinese Academy of Sciences, Kunming, KIZ2012005747, 65.2 mm standard length, Anshui Village, Lingyun County, Guangxi Zhuang Autonomous Region, China; 
<geoCoordinate id="E10A11EB1100ECBAFF14DE87C2F96F2B" direction="north" orientation="latitude" precision="5" value="24.3632">24.3632N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate id="625403CF6079411673CB63E03C8FC622" direction="east" orientation="longitude" precision="5" value="106.7412">106.7412E</geoCoordinate>
